    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> basa fillets</strong> to the<strong> spice mix </strong>and turn them several times until they're fully coated in all the spices – this is your <strong>coated basa</strong></p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated basa</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until cooked through – this is your <strong>spiced basa</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
