    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the basa is cooking, roll the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
